{"tid":1019191,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港喜茶真心不了","createTime":"2019-02-12T19:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T01:31:36.000Z","uid":141179,"like":5,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb2d2a174fee7fb84fc03cac29068a38fb06e7f","tid":1019191,"uid":141179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"前幾日試飲沙田間喜茶<br />\n見人少少咪排下睇下佢同大陸個間有咩分別<br />\n以為香港個間會正啲，點知......<br />\n本身冇得手機落單不在話下啦<br />\n搞到要不停mon住幾時先到自己<br />\n終於等到自己個no.<br />\n竟然可以係拎茶個陣，原來個order係未整好<br />\n成堆人就企晒係拎茶位到等<br />\n出一杯唔出一杯<br />\n見住個妹妹仔等左成粒鐘有多<br />\n（講緊既係當時叫到770以上，而佢係74幾）<br />\n然後有啲77幾既人係拎到茶<br />\n但好多767574既都未拎得<br />\n試過飲內地個間（唔知係咪間間都咁）<br />\n但起碼人地真係跟番個no.出<br />\n等好耐先拎到杯野<br />\n芝芝分量少、味道又差啲<br />\n價錢又貴<br />\n真心不了"},{"pid":"9ea0cb27284f5c009cf2fb0559d8f0bc668f3e9a","tid":1019191,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9480876d852f87fea3bce49185951ba937e63358","tid":1019191,"uid":7820,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:21:57.000Z","msg":"on9先飲 內你老母地<br />\n死返支那啦"},{"pid":"6bae752a7341cadb512c924e3ca58947d8321916","tid":1019191,"uid":22756,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:23:20.000Z","msg":"去支那飲啦屌"},{"pid":"1a5bd5b6fe928c726e4c2c7cd61a72f6f712efc8","tid":1019191,"uid":30395,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:25:33.000Z","msg":"你飲已經係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9acb30543431f3ddb9f486425b3f13f42c96b2b","tid":1019191,"uid":90820,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T19:29:21.000Z","msg":"喜茶本身已經戇鳩<br />\n唔關中國定香港事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你重講得出香港同中國喜茶嘅分別<br />\n好明顯飲開<br />\n戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f1ca98df883775789494e5489e6da0bd498d28","tid":1019191,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislik